Configuration is done through the use of a Windows utility bundled with the device.
Sold by Pheobe Micro [http://www.phoebemicro.com/download/wireless.php as the PHWL11-AP].
Default credentials are from Phoebe Micro's manual for the PHWL11-AP. The manual also states there is a read only access password of '''public'''. The OUI commonly used by the item is probably 00:90:96 (most common for the SSID in WiGLE).
